      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770442657972,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Bit.ly - url shortner\n\nFR:\n1. given a long url, a short url should be returned\n2. using a short url, user should be able to be redirected to the original url\n\nNFR:\n1. Availability > Consistency (available 99.99% of time)\n2. Uniqueness of short code to be ensured\n2. low latency redirect\n3. scale - supposing a high scale company - we would be supporting 100 M urls\n4. should be stored for long time\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Bit.ly - url shortner\n\nFR:\n1. given a long url, a short url should be returned\n2. using a short url, user should be able to be redirected to the original url\n\nNFR:\n1. Availability > Consistency (available 99.99% of time)\n2. Uniqueness of short code to be ensured\n2. low latency redirect\n3. scale - supposing a high scale company - we would be supporting 100 M urls\n4. should be stored for long time\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
