      "originalText": "FB New Feed\n\nUsers can post and see others posts, it will be a \nread heavy system as users might post once a day but\nwill see a lot many posts throughout the day\n\nFR:\n1. user should be able to create a post\n2. user should be able to see their timeline(news feed)\n3. ",
